궁극의 교육 플랫폼? AI 기업으로 진화한 듀오링고(DUOL)의 놀라운 실적 및 주가
description:
듀오링고(Duolingo)의 2025년 1분기 실적이 공개됐습니다. 매출 2억 3,070만 달러, 하루 활성 사용자 4,660만 명, 주가는 무려 21.6% 상승!  

하지만 진짜 중요한 건 이 회사의 정체성이 바뀌고 있다는 겁니다. 이제 듀오링고는 단순한 언어 학습 앱이 아니라, AI 중심 교육 플랫폼으로 진화하고 있죠.

Duolingo Max 유료화 전략부터 생성형 AI를 활용한 콘텐츠 자동화, 그리고 음악·수학·체스 과목까지 확장한 비즈니스 모델 변화까지—이 영상에서 자세히 분석해드립니다.

#듀오링고 #Duolingo실적 #AI교육플랫폼 #미국주식 #DuolingoMax #주가분석 #미국성장주 #교육앱 #AI기업 #투자정보 #DUOL

본 콘텐츠는 투자에 대한 조언을 제공하기 위한 목적이 아니며, 작성자의 개인적인 의견과 분석을 바탕으로 한 정보 제공용입니다. 투자 결정에 따른 책임은 전적으로 투자자 본인에게 있으며, 콘텐츠 제작자는 어떠한 손실에 대해서도 책임지지 않습니다. 투자 전 반드시 본인의 판단과 추가적인 자료 확인이 필요합니다.

title: How to speak SPANISH in 3 seconds
Common Public Speaking Mistake to Avoid!
description:
You'll probably make this mistake if you're new to public speaking.

It's a natural reaction to step back when you feel nervous so if you want to avoid coming across as nervous then plant your feet when you speak!

#publicspeaking #communicationskills

The 3-2-1 Speaking Trick That Forces You To Stop Rambling!
description:
In this video you'll learn a powerful communication framework that helps you stop rambling and speak with clarity & confidence under pressure.

FREE 3 Part Video Series ➡ https://gifts.vinhgiang.com/youtube
A self-guided 3 part video series to uncover communication habits holding you back

FREE Art of Conversation Training ➡ https://bit.ly/3XeCgvC
I'll teach you 3 communication frameworks to master conversations 🗣️

Join 1.5M+ readers receiving my weekly newsletter  ➡ https://bit.ly/4dewdxU

Join the STAGE Academy (my online course) ➡ https://bit.ly/3IPjHJW

When you use communication frameworks, it distills your messy mind into a clear structure. That's why they're so powerful!

When you're put on the spot to speak and you feel the pressure to give a good answer, without frameworks, you ramble and speak your messy thoughts out loud. This comes across unclear, and lacking in authority and confidence.

The 3-2-1 framework is a powerful yet simple way to combat rambling, by simply distilling your thinking into a listicle, either 3 steps, 2 types, or the 1 thing.

Now instead of blurting out mumbo jumbo you're now speaking in clear points in the moment. This is extremely powerful when you haven't prepared anything to talk about or someone puts you on the spot, like in a job interview, in a team meeting or in every day conversations.

=== About Vinh Giang ===
Vinh Giang is an internationally acclaimed keynote speaker, communication skills expert, and magician. He blends his unique talents to captivate audiences and deliver powerful lessons on the art of influence, persuasion, and effective communication. His mission is to empower individuals and leaders to communicate with clarity, confidence, and impact, enabling them to unlock new levels of success in both their personal and professional lives.

title: Practice English Speaking with Shadowing | Learn English Conversation Fast 💬
description:
Do you want to speak English better and faster? This video will help you practice listening, learn new words and expressions, and improve your speaking skills. You can watch this video many times to master the vocabulary and expressions you learn today. At the end, we will do Shadowing Practice together to sound more natural in English. 🎧🗣️

Download Shadowing Audio+PDF Lessons here 👉 https://englisheasypractice.com/speaking-course-shadowing/

👉 Part 1: Listening to English Conversation
In the first part, you will listen to a simple English conversation. Listening is very important because it helps you understand real English in daily life. Don’t worry if you don’t understand everything the first time. Just listen carefully and enjoy the story.

👉 Part 2: Learn Vocabulary
Next, we will learn some useful vocabulary and expressions from the conversation. For example, you will learn the expression “That reminds me of”, and how people use it in daily English. You will also learn the word “puddle” and other easy words. We will give you short example sentences so you can remember them better. 📖✨

👉 Part 3: English-Speaking Practice
After learning the vocabulary, it’s time to practice speaking! In this part, you will answer easy questions about the conversation. Speaking out loud is the best way to improve fluency. Don’t be shy — repeat after me and speak clearly. This will help you build confidence. 💬💪

Download listen-and-answer practice lessons here 👉 https://englisheasypractice.com/

👉 Part 4: Shadowing Practice
Finally, we will do Shadowing Practice. Shadowing means listening and speaking at the same time. You will listen to my voice and repeat the sentences quickly, just like an echo. This method helps you improve pronunciation, rhythm, and speed. With practice, your English will sound more natural. 🎤🎶
